多得多了，这是真的吗？她是不是在怕我担心而安慰我？"},"attached_info":"Cj4Ig5jj3uKK5FEQAxoINjQ2OTc2OTkgy5+khQYwJTioDEARcgk0NjA4ODE0ODd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"161 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-5660f4624c17c100b6d3d0ff84644e73_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"18_1621976811.3895998","card_id":"Q_461134288","target":{"id":461134288,"title":"如何看待 BeryL 在 2021 季中赛决赛决胜局塔姆三级不点 W 导致下路送出一血？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/461134288","type":"question","created":1621833338,"answer_count":21,"follower_count":64,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[18427,451855,713590,725161,727250],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"三级点出 QQE 而非三个技能全部解锁。"},"attached_info":"Cj0Ig5jj3uKK5FEQAxoINjQ3NTM5MTQg+uyshQYwADhAQBJyCTQ2MTEzNDI4OHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"160 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picb.zhimg.com/50/v2-9e0957bb7fad8de14428f4a923a724c0_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"19_1621976811.3899744","card_id":"Q_459925498","target":{"id":459925498,"title":"为什么从市场表现来看，中国半导体行业不害怕美国制裁？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/459925498","type":"question","created":1621234323,"answer_count":30,"follower_count":292,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[922,10722,33564,90716,411537],"comment_count":2,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"2018年4月，美国商务部宣布未来七年禁止向中兴通讯出售任何电子技术和通讯元件，自那以后，中国芯片行业经历了前所未有的三年。 据《财经》2021年1月4日报道，2018年－2020年，三年间中国半导体的投资额超过了前10年的总和。 第三方数据分析机构清科的数据显示，2018年，中国半导体投资额为61.27亿元；2019年增长了6倍，为398.85亿元；2020年上半年，半导体以548.15亿元的投资规模超过互联网，成为最吸金的行业，中科创星创始合伙人米磊称之为“历史性的拐点”。 根据天眼查统计，2019年注册在案的芯片企业为53238家，2020年为59793家，是2014年的近5倍，比10年前增加了近